headline: Autodesk (ADSK) Q4 2026 Earnings Call Transcript
summary: As demonstrated at Autodesk University and our Investor Day, and reflected in our results today, we remain well positioned to deliver for Autodesk, Inc. customers and investors.  While initiatives like this are difficult and complex, they are making Autodesk, Inc. more resilient and unlocking new avenues for growth and margin expansion.  In the coming months, Autodesk, Inc. will roll out powerful AI capabilities built on a combination of frontier models and our proprietary models that understand 3D design and make.
